<article id="main-content" data-history-node-id="343" class="node node--type-species-item node--view-mode-full">
        
  <div class="node__content">

      
          
    
      
              
  <div class="wwf-phs-container  paragraph-container ">
  <div id="wwf-phs-id">
    <div class="wwf-phs-slide  grid grid-cols-2">
      <div class="wwf-phs-content-left ">
        <div class="wwf-phs-border ">
          <h1>The snow leopard: elegant and elusive</h1>
          <p><p>By protecting the rare snow leopard we’re also helping to protect its whole environment.</p>
</p>


          

