                  <a class="anchor_link " href="#how-were-helping-snow-leopards" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #how-were-helping-snow-leopards" ga-event-label=" The snow leopard: elegant and elusive  How we&#039;re helping">How we&#039;re helping</a>
                  <a class="anchor_link " href="#adoption_panel" ga-on="click" ga-event-category="CTAButton" ga-event-action="click - #adoption_panel" ga-event-label=" The snow leopard: elegant and elusive  Adopt a Snow leopard">Adopt a Snow leopard</a>
                          <span class="btn share_container" onclick="">
